  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Software Tester",
  "description": "<p></p><h3>Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Review requirements and user stories to create test cases, scenarios, and test data</p></li><li><p>Perform manual testing to ensure applications meet functional and business requirements</p></li><li><p>Identify, log, and track defects clearly and accurately</p></li><li><p>Work closely with developers to troubleshoot issues and improve product quality</p></li><li><p>Test applications even when documentation is incomplete and highlight potential risks</p></li><li><p>View issues from an end-user perspective and suggest improvements to user experience</p></li><li><p>Maintain test documentation and support continuous improvement of QA processes</p></li><li><p>Participate in daily stand-ups and team meetings</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Diploma or Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, IT, or related field (or equivalent experience)</p></li><li><p>Basic understanding of SDLC and software testing principles</p></li><li><p>Ability to analyze requirements and design test scenarios</p></li><li><p>Strong attention to detail and analytical thinking</p></li><li><p>Team player with a positive learning attitude</p></li><li><p>1–2 years of software testing experience is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Exposure to automation tools (e.g. Selenium) or scripting (e.g. Python) is a plus</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Please email a copy of your detailed resume to <strong>chally@talentsis.com.sg </strong>for immediate processing.</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
